GSD.description:
ipv4: prevent potential spectre v1 gadget in fib_metrics_match()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.166 by commit 7f9828fb1f688210e681268490576f0ca65c322a, it was introduced in version v4.14 by commit 5f9ae3d9e7e4ad6db0491abc7c4ae5452dbeadd8. For more details please see the references link.
